About Us
Who we are
Hidden Fairway was born out of necessity. After the closing of  Golf Grove on Bearss, we were left without any local driving ranges open after 6pm. That’s where we come in. We are an indoor driving range that is capped at 35 members in the heart of North Hyde Park. We offer a way for golfers to pre book sessions and practice in a controlled environment.

Special Events
Hidden Fairway is available for parties, corporate events, or any special occasion. Guests will have full access to the facilities and extended time. A member of our staff will be more than happy to provide a tour if you have not visited before, and they will also be available on the day of the event to ensure that everything is set up correctly. After that, the space is all yours.
Most events can be booked 10-14 days in advance. Our standard booking rates are $100 per hour with a 2-hour minimum.
Please contact us with the details of your event, and we will respond to your inquiry shortly.
